Interface DimensionField<T extends CommonIndexValue>

  • Type Parameters:

    public interface DimensionField<T extends CommonIndexValue>
extends NumericDimensionDefinition
    This interface provides in addition to the index dimension definition, a way to read and write a field and get a field ID
